creator: Presto Eat
descriptionHtml:
Presto Eat has just landed in Tripoli !
Order from our wide range of restaurants and definitely your favourite is among them, just download the app.

About the app:

Our services is on demand that means when you are starving and hungry you do not need to worry about rush hours nor traffic nor the PrestoMan having other customers to drive to. PrestoMan will only drive to pick your order and then straight to you. You know what that means? Your order will reach as fast as you can count to 10 😮. That does not end here with our Tracking feature you will know your order status whether it was being prepared or is it on the way to you by PrestoMan. Our PrestoMan is equipped with Heat Preservers so your food can reach you HOT 🔥 also with our toppings feature you can control what is in your order.

Our Restaurants:
We provide you with more than 100 restaurants across Tripoli, you want a Burger, Pizza, Sea Food, Traditional, Shawarma, Fancy or Breakfast it is all presented to you throughout the day. You can use our in app features and filters to decide by the type of the food you want given your personal desires, you also can see the most popular restaurants in your area rated by our customers, not to mention that you can add your favourite restaurants to a list so you can easily order from them every time you enter the app.

The Wallet feature:
With our wallet feature you can add up to your wallet and avoid paying in cash everytime you order.

Promotional Codes:
You can get discounts by using promotional codes we share with you across our social media platforms.

You can smoothly change between your locations:
Either you were at work, home or with friends you can easily change between your locations and your order will reach you without any problem such as mentioning the address to the PrestoMan again and again.

Presto is the on-demand delivery app that brings you the best of your city, right to your door and the fastest and most convenient way to order food and groceries. With our wide selection of restaurants and grocery items, you can find everything you need, all in one place. 📲🚀

Explore many features with Presto such as:
- Ordering food and groceries from your favorite restaurants and our warehouses. 🍔🍟🍕🍪🍫🥦🍎
- Track your order status in real time. 📍
- Pay with cash, Presto wallet, online payment methods and more 💰💳
- Get exclusive deals and discounts on items and meals 🤩
- Customer support before during and after your order ☎

* How to order from Presto:
1. Download the app.
2. Create an account.
3. Browse the menu of your favorite restaurant (PrestoEat) or items and groceries (PrestoJet).
4. Add items to your cart and checkout.
5. Track your order status and receive it at your door.

Download Presto today and start enjoying the best of your city, delivered right to your door! 😎✨
